  "texts": [
    "We then compute the average of the bias power spectra obtained from 500 simulations to estimate the actual bias power spectra.",
    "These bias power spectra are then used appropriately in the L1, L2 and L3 models according to our specific needs as described in Section 4.6.",
    "ResultsWe plot the delensing fraction in Fig. 7.",
    "We observe good consistency between the two methods for both experiments.",
    "However, the inverse-lensing method yields slightly higher values compared to the template method, this is due to the noise bias introduced during the delensing procedure, as discussed in 2.3.3."
